    dc:description "FIGURE 18. Xenylla duchesnea, lectotype. A) Dorsal chaetotaxy. B) Ventral cephalic chaetotaxy. C) Ventral chaetotaxy of abdominal segments II ‒ V. D) Labial palpus. E) Third and fourth antennal segments, dorsal view. F) Third and fourth antennal segments, ventral view. G) Foretibiotarsus, dorsal view. H) Retinaculum and furcula." ;
